text: Corquoy is a commune in Cher, Centre-Val de Loire, France. The former commune Sainte-Lunaise was merged into Corquoy on 1 January 2019.Arrêté préfectoral 27 September 2018 , p. 260 About 203 people lived there in January 2019. ==Population== ==References== Category:Communes in Cher
